OL,5, Scotland's top law officer is seeking a
OL,6, change in the rules on evidence which  
OL,7, could allow far more prosecutions to be
OL,8, brought in rape cases.                 
OL,10,FIn a rare legal move, Lord Advocate    
OL,11,FDorothy Bain has asked the appeal court
OL,12,Fto overturn a ruling made by five      
OL,13,Fjudges in 1997.                        
OL,15,FThe case is being heard by a panel of  
OL,16,Fseven judges.                          
OL,18,FAnother senior lawyer is in court      
OL,19,Fopposing the move, arguing the change  
OL,20,Fcould lead to wrongful convictions.    
